>>> info

This method has its name changed from vanilla: `getType`.
In KubeJS, [[ref/utils/EntityKJS|`getType`]] refers to a more script-friendly method that returns the entity's ID as string. It comes from the [[ref/utils/EntityKJS|`EntityKJS`]] interface.

<<<

