- `[js]uuid`: A [universally unique identifier (UUID)](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/21/docs/api/java.base/java/util/UUID.html) to set. It may be a string representing a UUID, for example `[js]'9839ba5f-87fa-4718-aeab-f2b6d74a2385'`.

**Getter return value**
A [universally unique identifier (UUID)](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/21/docs/api/java.base/java/util/UUID.html) of the entity.
